item.description: Let's have a game of volleyball on a nice afternoon. We will set up the net at 3:30pm. Please brings rakes if you have them. We may even take a swim so bring your bathing suit. New people are always welcome. Kids are welcome too. Hope to see you there! Let me know if you want to do this again on a Sunday.
item.how_to_find_us: We will be there setting up the volleyball net! Let us know you are there and we will welcome you!
